{"tid":1871329,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急!!] 呼籲食肆即時停售水煙 播毒！","createTime":"2020-02-09T11:26:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-09T11:44:27.000Z","uid":272125,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3e0d0eab9088c9ccbaf35843bee22025d8af0de5","tid":1871329,"uid":272125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T11:26:05.000Z","msg":"公開呼籲食肆即時停售水煙 以免病毒傳播 疫症風險<br />\n<br />\n最近中國武漢肺炎傳染病疫情擴散，由於吸食水煙需要將水加熱作為吸食媒介，吸食過程中會衍生由吸食水煙人士呼出帶有水分子空氣(即氣溶膠)。近日根據國家衛生部及其他國家科學研究，發現氣溶膠乃本次中國武漢肺炎疫情傳播途徑之一 。 <br />\n所謂&quot;氣溶膠傳播&quot;，即飛沫混合在空氣中，形成&quot;氣溶膠&quot;，吸入後導致感染。<br />\n<br />\n如果有傳染病患者吸食水煙，水煙煙霧或極可能成為傳染病的傳播媒介，危害市民健康安全。<br />\n<br />\n另外根據星島日報的報道，呼吸系統科專科醫生提醒市民無法知悉水煙成分的危險性，加上吸食水煙者往往會共食一壺，增加了患傳染病風險，包括乙型和丙型肝炎，中國武漢肺炎傳染病有可能根據這個途徑擴散。<br />\n<br />\n故此要求有關食肆立即採取適當措施，停售水煙以保市民健康。<br />\n<br />\nBBC武漢肺炎：中國確認新冠病毒經空氣通過氣溶膠傳染<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-51427216\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-51427216&d=HBevYr6AXW9Qrc%2FJEBnfqjbcp9x5SJfJ3tUQBIbvNjo%3D&h=c4eda4eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-51427216&h=d78dcf65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-51427216</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n星島日報報道<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A6%82%E9%A6%99%E7%85%99%E9%87%8B%E7%99%8C%E7%89%A9-%E5%90%B8%E6%B0%B4%E7%85%99%E5%8B%BF%E7%95%B6%E7%8E%A9%E6%84%8F-215530294.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25A6%2582%25E9%25A6%2599%25E7%2585%2599%25E9%2587%258B%25E7%2599%258C%25E7%2589%25A9-%25E5%2590%25B8%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E7%2585%2599%25E5%258B%25BF%25E7%2595%25B6%25E7%258E%25A9%25E6%2584%258F-215530294.html&d=HBevYr6AXW9Qrc%2FJEBnfqjbcp9x5SJfJ3tUQBIbvNjo%3D&h=5d3b37d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A6%82%E9%A6%99%E7%85%99%E9%87%8B%E7%99%8C%E7%89%A9-%E5%90%B8%E6%B0%B4%E7%85%99%E5%8B%BF%E7%95%B6%E7%8E%A9%E6%84%8F-215530294.html</a>"},{"pid":"b227e02e6492d8deeec413328b161c3bdcb33bca","tid":1871329,"uid":120918,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T11:34:37.000Z","msg":"樓豬毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?<br />\n唔講咁多<br />\n即刻同班fd chill一chill<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"688f95abd2b34ba2a2d3be0b923530931a62e2bd","tid":1871329,"uid":190789,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T11:36:00.000Z","msg":"要死啲弱智"},{"pid":"4d4a1f4331f7976333e2f5f64e037b1c37c711a8","tid":1871329,"uid":124021,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T11:36:26.000Z","msg":"食煙嗰班都唔驚肺癌，會驚你個區區肺炎？"},{"pid":"e5e0d8632106c8bdac043cd1acd099a80d516466","tid":1871329,"uid":177326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T11:38:48.000Z","msg":"求問有肺炎既人吸煙個陣呼D氣出黎，個D氣噴到我會唔會好易出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3b83b5045d553f46a583e6f6206fb35cc2d46b","tid":1871329,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T11:39:22.000Z","msg":"食得個班都係MK 傻閪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba851e61d772cd29ae77aa58a156516ba6e46c1","tid":1871329,"uid":156327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T11:39:48.000Z","msg":"諾士佛台咪好撚毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb09f91a33fe9118851daf0b7b8a1179c9b627d","tid":1871329,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T11:40:56.000Z","msg":"自己死唔係問題 唔好累人"},{"pid":"0e7ee1ca2b5ca8dd46e7263b07e06acb80e1f933","tid":1871329,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T11:44:01.000Z","msg":"食煙會削弱扺抗力，點解唔一刀切禁晒佢？"},{"pid":"cc31cfacbf436